Description

Interface for User Account Business Operations.
UserAccountBusinessService
User Account Business level Service that Implements UserDetailService.

UserAccountEntity
User Account Entity Object used for Data Level operations.
UserAccountModel
User Account Model Object used for Business Level operations.

UserAccount Repository object which extends CrudRepository with types UserAccountEntity and Long.
UserAccountRowMapper

UserLoginController
Spring Controller that returns the login view for Spring Security.
